config.section.= WELCOME! =.name: = WELCOME! =
config.Highlight Texts For More Info!.de: = Have A Fantastic Day & Happy Fishing! =
config.Disable Yearly Developer Gifts.de: This setting will disable the mod developer gifts you will receive yearly. By default, you will receive a yearly randomized gift from myself :-)
config.Fishing Difficulty.name: Fishing Difficulty
config.Fishing Difficulty.description: Select a difficulty setting for the fishing minigame. Easy Settings: Decrease difficulty by 5% to 100%. Easy Sunday Fishing: Decrease difficulty by 10% to 30% on Sundays only. Hard Settings: Increase difficulty by 5% to 100% with a NIGHTMARE option for those seeking the ultimate challenge! For details on the Dynamic Weather settings, highlight the 'Dynamic Weather Info' below for more information. Scroll down for additional options.
config.section.Fishing Minigame.name: Fishing Minigame
config.= Dynamic Weather Info =.name: = Dynamic Weather Info =
config.= Dynamic Weather Info =.descript: If you select a Dynamic Weather setting for Fishing Difficulty, this will change fishing difficulty based on the weather. The settings are as follows; Easy Setting: Wind = 15% Harder, Rain = 10% Easier, Snow = 15% Easier, Storm = 20% Easier. The Easier option will make those options easier by another 10% and Easiest by another 20%.
config.All Times Of Day.name: All Times Of Day
config.All Times Of Day.description: All fish are now catchable at any time of day.
config.All Types Of Weather.name: All Types Of Weather
config.All Types Of Weather.description: All fish, except legendary fish, can now be caught in all types of weather.
config.All Seasons.name: All Seasons
config.All Seasons.description: All fish, except legendary fish, can now be caught in every season.
config.Same Spawn Rates.name: Same Spawn Rates
config.Same Spawn Rates.description: All fish, except legendary fish, now share the same spawn rates.
config.Clean Waters/No Trash.name: Clean Waters/No Trash
config.Clean Waters/No Trash.description: Select a setting to remove or replace all trash items while fishing. No Trash: Disables trash while fishing entirely. Crab Pot Fish: Replaces trash items with crab pot fish during fishing. Note that occasional trash items may still be fished up. Trash serves as a fallback if no fish spawn, but these settings significantly reduce trash chances.
config.Clean Waters/No Weeds.name: Clean Waters/No Weeds
config.Clean Waters/No Weeds.description: Select a setting to remove or replace Seaweed, Green Algae, and White Algae while fishing. No Weeds and Algae: Disables all weeds and algae while fishing entirely. Crab Pot Fish: Replaces seaweed and algae with crab pot fish during fishing.
config.Crab Pots No Trash.name: Crab Pots No Trash
config.Crab Pots No Trash.description: Crab Pots will no longer yield trash items, but there remains a small chance of obtaining Broken Glasses and CDs.
config.section.Crab Pot Fishing.name: Crab Pot Fishing
config.Crab Pots Bug Meat.name: Crab Pots Bug Meat
config.Crab Pots Bug Meat.description: Crab Pots now spawn Bug Meat. Choose whether they can spawn in freshwater (rivers and lakes) or the ocean (beach).
config.Fish Sell Value.name: Fish Sell Value
config.Fish Sell Value.description: Select the sell value of all fish (except legendary fish). The range is from 10% to 1000% increase. Refer to the Legendary Fish Sell Values setting below to do the same for legendary fish. Note that enabling or disabling these settings affects newly acquired fish after your chosen setting is enabled. Scroll down for additional options.
config.section.Value of Fishing.name: Value of Fishing
config.Seasonal Fish On Farm.name: Seasonal Fish On Farm
config.Seasonal Fish On Farm.description: Seasonal Fish are now catchable on the farm, across all farm maps.
config.section.Farmland Fishing.name: Farmland Fishing
config.Specialty Fish On Farm.name: Specialty Fish On Farm
config.Specialty Fish On Farm.descriptio: Specialty Fish are now catchable on the farm, across all farm maps.
config.Legendary Fish On Farm.name: Legendary Fish On Farm
config.Legendary Fish On Farm.descriptio: Legendary Fish are now catchable on the farm, across all farm maps. Only one legendary fish can be caught on a farm map unless you enable the 'Recatch Legendary Fish' option which will allow you to catch more than one.
config.Recatch Legendary Fish.name: Recatch Legendary Fish
config.Recatch Legendary Fish.descriptio: Legendary fish can now be caught multiple times.
config.section.Legendary Fishing.name: Legendary Fishing
config.Entire Area Legendary Fish.name: Entire Area Legendary Fish
config.Entire Area Legendary Fish.descri: Legendary fish are no longer restricted to specific points on the map; they can now be caught anywhere within their residing area. For instance, the Crimsonfish can be found all around the beach, not solely at the eastern docks.
config.All Weather Legendary Fish.name: All Weather Legendary Fish
config.All Weather Legendary Fish.descri: Legendary fish can now be caught in all types of weather.
config.All Seasons Legendary Fish.name: All Seasons Legendary Fish
config.All Seasons Legendary Fish.descri: Legendary fish can now be caught in every season.
config.Legendary Quests (Recatch REQ).de: Unlock new quests related to legendary fish! Keep in mind that the ¡®Recatch Legendary Fish¡¯ setting must be enabled for this feature to function. Once you¡¯ve successfully caught a legendary fish and are in the appropriate season, these new quests will become available.
config.Legendary Fish Sell Value.name: Legendary Fish Sell Value
config.Legendary Fish Sell Value.descrip: Select the sell value of legendary fish. The range is from 10% to 1000% increase. Note that enabling or disabling these settings affects newly acquired legendary fish after your chosen setting is enabled. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Rare Legendary Fish.name: Rare Legendary Fish
config.Rare Legendary Fish.description: Select the rarity of legendary fish appearing while fishing.
config.Lucky Legendary Fish.name: Lucky Legendary Fish
config.Lucky Legendary Fish.description: Legendary fish now only spawn when daily luck from the TV is at its highest.
config.Curious Legendary Fish.name: Curious Legendary Fish
config.Curious Legendary Fish.descriptio: Select the effectiveness of the Curiosity Lure buff for Legendary Fish. This range spans from 10% to 100%. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Legendary Fish Gifts.name: Legendary Fish Gifts
config.Legendary Fish Gifts.description: Legendary fish are now a universally loved gift for all the villagers.
config.Legendary Fish 7am To 9am.name: Legendary Fish 7am To 9am
config.Legendary Fish 7am To 9am.descrip: Legendary fish are now exclusively accessible from 7AM to 9AM, and this time frame can be combined with the other time settings.
config.Legendary Fish 12pm To 2pm.name: Legendary Fish 12pm To 2pm
config.Legendary Fish 12pm To 2pm.descri: Legendary fish are now exclusively accessible from 12PM to 2PM, and this time frame can be combined with the other time settings.
config.Legendary Fish 11pm To 1am.name: Legendary Fish 11pm To 1am
config.Legendary Fish 11pm To 1am.descri: Legendary fish are now exclusively accessible from 11PM to 1AM, and this time frame can be combined with the other time settings.
config.Qi's Legendary Fish Icon.name: Qi's Legendary Fish Icon
config.Qi's Legendary Fish Icon.descript: The Legendary Fish that appear during Qi¡¯s Special Order Request will now be distinguished by the ¡®Boss Fish¡¯ icon in the fishing minigame.
config.Fish Pond Rare Loot.name: Fish Pond Rare Loot
config.Fish Pond Rare Loot.description: Select the likelihood of rare loot spawning from fish pond buildings. Options range from 2X to 5X increase. Alternatively, the Rare Loot Chance All 50% option ensures an equal chance for all rare loot from fish ponds to appear. Scroll down for additional options.
config.section.Fish Pond Buildings.name: Fish Pond Buildings
config.FP Fish/Quest Spawn Time.name: FP Fish/Quest Spawn Time
config.FP Fish/Quest Spawn Time.descript: Select the speed for fish reproduction and when new fish pond quests appear from fish pond buildings. These options will take effect only when the fish pond is empty, and you¡¯ve enabled the desired setting before adding fish.
config.Fish Pond Legendary Fish (REQ).de: Legendary fish can now be added to the fish pond buildings. This setting is required for the legendary fish pond settings below!
config.Legendary Fish Pond Loot.name: Legendary Fish Pond Loot
config.Legendary Fish Pond Loot.descript: Select the likelihood of legendary fish rare loot spawning from fish pond buildings. The available settings range from 2X to 5X increase. The Rare Loot Chance All 50% option ensures that all rare loot from fish ponds has an equal chance to spawn. Note: This feature requires the Fish Pond Legendary Fish (REQ) setting to be enabled!
config.LG Fish/Quest Spawn Time.name: LG Fish/Quest Spawn Time
config.LG Fish/Quest Spawn Time.descript: Select the speed for legendary fish reproduction and when new legendary fish pond quests appear from fish pond buildings. This feature requires the Fish Pond Legendary Fish (REQ) setting to be enabled! These options will take effect only when the fish pond is empty, and you¡¯ve enabled the desired setting before adding fish.
config.Fish Pond Prismatic Shards.name: Fish Pond Prismatic Shards
config.Fish Pond Prismatic Shards.descri: Every fish pond building now has the opportunity to yield Prismatic Shards when the fish ponds are at full capacity.
config.Tackle Materials.name: Tackle Materials
config.Tackle Materials.description: Reduce the material requirements for crafting tackle and lures.
config.Tackle Fishing Level 1.name: Tackle Fishing Level 1
config.Tackle Fishing Level 1.descriptio: All tackle can now be learned at Fishing Level 1.
config.Craftable Curiosity Lure.name: Craftable Curiosity Lure
config.Craftable Curiosity Lure.descript: The Curiosity Lure can now be crafted, and the recipe will be learned either at Fishing Level 9 or Level 1. This lure enhances the likelihood of rare fish spawning.
config.Curiosity Lure Materials.name: Curiosity Lure Materials
config.Curiosity Lure Materials.descript: Reduce the material requirements for crafting the Curiosity Lure. Note that this feature requires the Craftable Curiosity Lure setting to be enabled!
config.Wild Bait Crafting Materials.name: Wild Bait Crafting Materials
config.Wild Bait Crafting Materials.desc: Reduce the material requirements for crafting Wild Bait.
config.Trout Soup Duration.name: Trout Soup Duration
config.Trout Soup Duration.description: The Trout Soup food item buffs will now persist for a full day.
config.Trout Soup Level Boost.name: Trout Soup Level Boost
config.Trout Soup Level Boost.descriptio: Select the fishing level boost provided by the Trout Soup food item. By default, it grants a +1 level boost to fishing, but you can adjust it within a range of +2 to +50. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Trout Soup Ingredients.name: Trout Soup Ingredients
config.Trout Soup Ingredients.descriptio: Select an option to reduce the ingredient requirements for the Trout Soup recipe.
config.Chowder Duration.name: Chowder Duration
config.Chowder Duration.description: The Chowder food item buffs will now persist for a full day.
config.Chowder Level Boost.name: Chowder Level Boost
config.Chowder Level Boost.description: Select the fishing level boost provided by the Chowder food item. By default, it grants a +1 level boost to fishing, but you can adjust it within a range of +2 to +50. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Chowder Ingredients.name: Chowder Ingredients

config.Fish Taco Level Boost.description: Select the fishing level boost provided by the Fish Taco food item. By default, it grants a +2 level boost to fishing, but you can adjust it within a range of +3 to +50. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Fish Taco Ingredients.name: Fish Taco Ingredients

config.Escargot Duration.name: Escargot Duration
config.Escargot Duration.description: The Escargot food item buffs will now persist for a full day.
config.Escargot Level Boost.name: Escargot Level Boost
config.Escargot Level Boost.description: Select the fishing level boost provided by the Escargot food item. By default, it grants a +2 level boost to fishing, but you can adjust it within a range of +3 to +50. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Escargot Ingredients.name: Escargot Ingredients

config.Dish O' The Sea Duration.name: Dish O' The Sea Duration

config.Dish O' The Sea Level Boost.name: Dish O' The Sea Level Boost
config.Dish O' The Sea Level Boost.descr: Select the fishing level boost provided by the Dish O' The Sea food item. By default, it grants a +3 level boost to fishing, but you can adjust it within a range of +4 to +50. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Dish O' The Sea Fishing Level 1.n: Dish O' The Sea Fishing Level 1
config.Dish O' The Sea Fishing Level 1.d: The Dish O' The Sea recipe is now accessible at Fishing Level 1, rather than Level 3.

config.Dish O' The Sea Ingredients.descr: Select an option to reduce the ingredient requirements for the Dish O' The Sea recipe.

config.Fish Stew Level Boost.name: Fish Stew Level Boost
config.Fish Stew Level Boost.description: Select the fishing level boost provided by the Fish Stew food item. By default, it grants a +3 level boost to fishing, but you can adjust it within a range of +4 to +50. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Fish Stew Ingredients.name: Fish Stew Ingredients
config.Fish Stew Ingredients.description: Select an option to reduce the ingredient requirements for the Fish Stew recipe.
config.Lobster Bisque Duration.name: Lobster Bisque Duration

config.Lobster Bisque Level Boost.name: Lobster Bisque Level Boost
config.Lobster Bisque Level Boost.descri: Select the fishing level boost provided by the Lobster Bisque food item. By default, it grants a +3 level boost to fishing, but you can adjust it within a range of +4 to +50. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Lobster Bisque Ingredients.name: Lobster Bisque Ingredients
config.Lobster Bisque Ingredients.descri: Select an option to reduce the ingredient requirements for the Lobster Bisque recipe.
config.Seafoam Pudding Duration.name: Seafoam Pudding Duration
config.Seafoam Pudding Duration.descript: The Seafoam Pudding food item buffs will now persist for a full day.
config.Seafoam Pudding Level Boost.name: Seafoam Pudding Level Boost
config.Seafoam Pudding Level Boost.descr: Select the fishing level boost provided by the Seafoam Pudding food item. By default, it grants a +4 level boost to fishing, but you can adjust it within a range of +5 to +50. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Seafoam Pudding Fishing Level 1.d: The Seafoam Pudding recipe is now accessible at Fishing Level 1, rather than Level 9.
config.Seafoam Pudding Ingredients.name: Seafoam Pudding Ingredients
config.Seafoam Pudding Ingredients.descr: Reduce the ingredient requirements for the Seafoam Pudding recipe, allowing for a range of 1 to 25 of any fish.
config.Worm Bin Materials.name: Worm Bin Materials
config.Worm Bin Materials.description: Reduce the material requirements for crafting the Worm Bin machine.
config.section.Worm Bin Machinery.name: Worm Bin Machinery
config.Worm Bin Level Availability.name: Worm Bin Level Availability
config.Worm Bin Level Availability.descr: Select the fishing level at which you can learn the Worm Bin crafting recipe.
config.Worm Bin Bait Min Amount.name: Worm Bin Bait Min Amount
config.Worm Bin Bait Min Amount.descript: Select the minimum daily bait production from the Worm Bin, with options ranging from 2 to 100. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Worm Bin Bait Max Amount.name: Worm Bin Bait Max Amount
config.Worm Bin Bait Max Amount.descript: Select the maximum daily bait production from the Worm Bin, with options ranging from 6 to 100. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Worm Bin Wild Bait (REQ).name: Worm Bin Wild Bait (REQ)
config.Worm Bin Wild Bait (REQ).descript: Worm Bins now possess a slight chance of producing Wild Bait. This feature is essential for configuring the Wild Bait settings below!
config.Worm Bin Wild Bait Chance.name: Worm Bin Wild Bait Chance
config.Worm Bin Wild Bait Chance.descrip: Select the probability of daily Wild Bait production from the Worm Bin. The available range spans from 15% to 100% chance. Note that this feature requires the Worm Bin Chance For Wild Bait (REQ) setting to be enabled! Scroll down for additional options.
config.Worm Bin Wild Bait Min Amount.nam: Worm Bin Wild Bait Min Amount
config.Worm Bin Wild Bait Min Amount.des: Select the minimum daily production of Wild Bait from the Worm Bin, with a range spanning from 2 to 100. Note that this feature requires the Worm Bin Chance For Wild Bait (REQ) setting to be enabled! Scroll down for additional options.
config.Worm Bin Wild Bait Max Amount.nam: Worm Bin Wild Bait Max Amount
config.Worm Bin Wild Bait Max Amount.des: Select the maximum daily production of Wild Bait from the Worm Bin, with a range spanning from 6 to 100. Note that this feature requires the Worm Bin Chance For Wild Bait (REQ) setting to be enabled! Scroll down for additional options.
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Materials.name: Deluxe Worm Bin Materials
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Materials.descrip: Reduce the material requirements for crafting the Deluxe Worm Bin machine.
Select the fishing level at which you can learn the Deluxe Worm Bin crafting recipe.
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Bait Min.name: Deluxe Worm Bin Bait Min
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Bait Min.descript: Select the minimum daily bait production from the Deluxe Worm Bin, with options ranging from 2 to 100. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Bait Max.name: Deluxe Worm Bin Bait Max
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Bait Max.descript: Select the maximum daily bait production from the Deluxe Worm Bin, with options ranging from 6 to 100. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Wild Bait (REQ).d: Deluxe Worm Bins now possess a slight chance of producing Wild Bait. This feature is essential for configuring the Wild Bait settings below!
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Wild B. Chance.na: Deluxe Worm Bin Wild B. Chance
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Wild B. Chance.de: Select the probability of daily Wild Bait production from the Deluxe Worm Bin. The available range spans from 15% to 100% chance. Note that this feature requires the Deluxe Worm Bin Chance For Wild Bait (REQ) setting to be enabled! Scroll down for additional options.
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Wild Bait Min.nam: Deluxe Worm Bin Wild Bait Min
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Wild Bait Min.des: Select the minimum daily production of Wild Bait from the Deluxe Worm Bin, with a range spanning from 2 to 100. Note that this feature requires the Deluxe Worm Bin Chance For Wild Bait (REQ) setting to be enabled! Scroll down for additional options.
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Wild Bait Max.nam: Deluxe Worm Bin Wild Bait Max
config.Deluxe Worm Bin Wild Bait Max.des: Select the maximum daily production of Wild Bait from the Deluxe Worm Bin, with a range spanning from 6 to 100. Note that this feature requires the Deluxe Worm Bin Chance For Wild Bait (REQ) setting to be enabled! Scroll down for additional options.
config.Recycling Machine Faster.name: Recycling Machine Faster
config.Recycling Machine Faster.descript: Reduce the production time for Recycling Machines, with options ranging from 50 minutes to 10 minutes. Scroll down for additional options.
config.section.Recycling Machine.name: Recycling Machine
config.Recycling Machine Materials.name: Recycling Machine Materials
config.Recycling Machine Materials.descr: Reduce the material requirements for crafting Recycling Machines.
config.Recycling Machine Level Avail..de: Select the fishing level at which you can acquire the Recycling Machine crafting recipe.
config.Recycling Machine Tackle.name: Recycling Machine Tackle
config.Recycling Machine Tackle.descript: Recycling Machines will now occasionally yield fishing tackle from all trash items.
config.Recycling Prismatic Shards.name: Recycling Prismatic Shards
config.Recycling Prismatic Shards.descri: Recycling Machines now have a slight chance of yielding a Prismatic Shard from trash items.
config.Fish Shop Open All Days.name: Fish Shop Open All Days
config.Fish Shop Open All Days.descripti: Willy¡¯s Fishing Shop will now remain open every day, except during special event days.
config.Crab Pot Price.name: Crab Pot Price
config.Crab Pot Price.description: Select the price of crab pots at Willy¡¯s Fishing Shop. The available range spans from 1g to 3000g. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Iridium Fishing Rod Level 1.name: Iridium Fishing Rod Level 1
config.Iridium Fishing Rod Level 1.descr: The Iridium Fishing Rod will now be offered for sale at Fishing Level 1 in Willy¡¯s Fishing Shop.
config.All Fishing Rod Prices.name: All Fishing Rod Prices
config.All Fishing Rod Prices.descriptio: Select the price of the Iridium Fishing Rod at Willy¡¯s Fishing Shop. The available range spans from 25% to 100% cheaper, or from 25% to 100% more expensive. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Fishing Shop Curiosity/Quality.de: Willy¡¯s Fishing Shop now sells the Curiosity and Quality lures for sale. These lures become available once you reach Fishing Level 9.
config.All Tackle Fishing Level 1.name: All Tackle Fishing Level 1
config.All Tackle Fishing Level 1.descri: At Fishing Level 1, all tackle is now available for sale at Willy¡¯s Fishing Shop.
config.Fishing Shop Tackle Prices.name: Fishing Shop Tackle Prices
config.Fishing Shop Tackle Prices.descri: Select the sale price of all lures at Willy¡¯s Fishing Shop. This range spans from 25% to 99% cheaper, or from 25% to 100% more expensive. Scroll down for additional options.
config.Fishing Shop Seafoam Pudding.name: Fishing Shop Seafoam Pudding
config.Fishing Shop Seafoam Pudding.desc: Willy¡¯s Fishing Shop now sells the Seafoam Pudding food item. You can decide whether to make it available at Fishing Level 9 or Level 1.
config.Fishing Shop Seafoam P Price.name: Fishing Shop Seafoam P Price
config.Fishing Shop Seafoam P Price.desc: Select the sale price of the Seafoam Pudding food item at Willy¡¯s Shop. This range spans from 4000g to 1g. Please note that the Fishing Shop Seafoam Pudding setting must be enabled for this to take effect! Scroll down for additional options.
config.Fishing Shop Worm Bin (REQ).name: Fishing Shop Worm Bin (REQ)
config.Fishing Shop Worm Bin (REQ).descr: Willy¡¯s Shop now sells the Worm Bin. This setting is essential for configuring the Worm Bin settings below!
config.Fishing Shop Worm Bin Price.name: Fishing Shop Worm Bin Price
config.Fishing Shop Worm Bin Price.descr: Select the sale price of the Worm Bin at Willy¡¯s Shop. This range spans from 4000g to 1g. Please note that the Fishing Shop Worm Bin (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect! Scroll down for additional options.
config.Fishing Shop Worm Bin Avail..name: Fishing Shop Worm Bin Avail.
config.Fishing Shop Worm Bin Avail..desc: Select the required fishing level for unlocking the Worm Bin at Willy¡¯s Shop. Please note that the Fishing Shop Worm Bin (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect! Scroll down for additional options.
config.Fish Shop Recycle Machine (REQ).d: Willy¡¯s Shop now sells the Recycling Machine. This setting is essential for configuring the Recycling Machine settings below!
config.Fish Shop Recycle Machine Price.d: Select the sale price of the Recycling Machine at Willy¡¯s Shop. This range spans from 3000g to 1g. Please note that the Fish Shop Recycle Machine (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect! Scroll down for additional options.
Select the required fishing level for unlocking the Recycling Machine at Willy¡¯s Shop. Please note that the Fish Shop Recycle Machine (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect!
config.Fishable Prismatic Shards (REQ).d: Prismatic Shards are now available for fishing and can be caught in most locations. This setting is essential for configuring most of the Prismatic Shard settings below!
config.Prismatic Shard Sell Value.name: Prismatic Shard Sell Value
config.Prismatic Shard Sell Value.descri: Select the sell value of Prismatic Shards. The default value is 2000g, but you can adjust it within a range from 1750g to 1g. Importantly, this setting operates independently and does not rely on any other Prismatic Shard configurations! Scroll down for additional options.
config.Prismatic Shards Fish Tanks.name: Prismatic Shards Fish Tanks
config.Prismatic Shards Fish Tanks.descr: Prismatic Shards can now be added to the aquarium fish tanks. Importantly, this setting operates independently and does not rely on any other Prismatic Shard configurations!
config.Prismatic Shard Spawn Rate.name: Prismatic Shard Spawn Rate
config.Prismatic Shard Spawn Rate.descri: Select the spawn rate of fishable Prismatic Shards. Please note that the Fishable Prismatic Shards (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect! Scroll down for additional options.
config.Prismatic Shards On Farm.name: Prismatic Shards On Farm
config.Prismatic Shards On Farm.descript: Prismatic Shards can now be caught on the farm, and this applies to all farm maps. Please note that the Fishable Prismatic Shards (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect!
config.Lucky Prismatic Shards.name: Lucky Prismatic Shards
config.Lucky Prismatic Shards.descriptio: The spawn rate of Prismatic Shards varies based on the daily luck reported by the TV. Please note that the Fishable Prismatic Shards (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect!
config.Prismatic Shards Weather.name: Prismatic Shards Weather
config.Prismatic Shards Weather.descript: Prismatic Shards are now exclusive to rainy and snowy weather for catching. Please note that the Fishable Prismatic Shards (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect!
config.Prismatic Shards 7am To 9am.name: Prismatic Shards 7am To 9am
config.Prismatic Shards 7am To 9am.descr: Prismatic Shards are now exclusive to the hours between 7AM and 9AM for catching, and this time frame can be combined with the other time settings. Please note that the Fishable Prismatic Shards (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect!
config.Prismatic Shards 12pm To 2pm.name: Prismatic Shards 12pm To 2pm
config.Prismatic Shards 12pm To 2pm.desc: Prismatic Shards are now exclusive to the hours between 12PM and 2PM for catching, and this time frame can be combined with the other time settings. Please note that the Fishable Prismatic Shards (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect!
config.Prismatic Shards 11pm To 1am.name: Prismatic Shards 11pm To 1am
config.Prismatic Shards 11pm To 1am.desc: Prismatic Shards are now exclusive to the hours between 11PM and 1AM for catching, and this time frame can be combined with the other time settings. Please note that the Fishable Prismatic Shards (REQ) setting must be enabled for this to take effect!

config.Pufferfish Exclusion.description: Pufferfish are now excluded from the fishing minigame. As a result, you will be limited to catching just one.
